## Line Plot
```python
fig, axis = plt.subplots()
fig.set_size_inches(10, 6)
plt.plot(data['Year'].values, data['Value'].values)
plt.xlabel('Year')
plt.ylabel(data['IndicatorName'].iloc[0], fontsize=10)
plt.title('Largest City pop %')
plt.axis([1959, 2015,0,30])
plt.show();
```
